text.tspan: Before you start your registration, there are a few steps you must complete first. Review these steps to
help ensure you set aside enough time to complete your registration.
Quick Start Guide for creating a login.gov account
Login.gov is a service that provides secure and private online access to government programs,
such as federal benefits, services, and applications. With a login.gov account, you can sign in to
multiple government websites (including SAM.gov) with the same username and password.
A login.gov account is required to register your entity in SAM. Once you complete the login.gov
authentication, return to SAM.gov to begin the registration process.
